outputs.output_descr: The first phase focused on needs assessment and system set-up. This second phase will start identifying the available and interested expatriate Iraqis to support the reconstruction of their country and deploy them.

project_descr: Building on the first phase of the Iraqis Rebuilding Iraq project, where the mechanisms of project implementation was set-up and needs were identified, this project focuses on identifying appropriate and interested Iraqi expatriates and their deployment.
